				<div id="maincontent">
		<div id="box_container">
									<div class="box nomargin">
				<h2>The Company</h2>
				Since 1948, our family-owned business has been supplying premium wholesale distributors with the highest quality berries and most flavorful varieties available in the industry. Grown, picked and packaged under the strictest quality standards, our produce goes from field to market with a minimal carbon footprint. Although we do not ship directly to end consumers, you can find our fresh, frozen and dried berries in stores across the country and around the world.			</div><!-- end box -->
			<div class="line_separator"></div>
									<div class="box">
				<h2>Taste The Difference</h2>
				The best berries begin with the best conditions...Oregon's climate and fertile soil give our berries a sweeter flavor than other berry-growing regions. Low humidity combined with warm summer days and cool, crisp nights enable Oregon-grown berries to hang on the bush for an extended period of time before harvesting is necessary. These conditions allow sugars to set, so that our berries can be harvested at the peak of flavor while retaining their firmness.			</div><!-- end box -->
									<div class="line_separator"></div>
			<div class="box">
				<h2>Who Grew My Berries?</h2>
				Oregon Berry Packing lets you pinpoint the source of your berries and even provides information about the specific variety that you have purchased.  <img src="http://www.oregonberry.com/wp-content/themes/blitz/images/bullseye.jpg" style="float: right;"><br>Just enter the lot code printed on your berries' container.

